#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:183
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Host name, Domainname, etc"
msgstr "ホスト名、ドメイン名等"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:187
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"One of the choices the user has to make is name his/her PC. This seems to be \n"
"quite easy, but <e>lots</e> of users are having difficulties finding the \n"
"appropriate name for their Linux-pc. To speed things up, know that any name you \n"
"choose can be changed afterwards. For all we care, you can just call your system\n"
"<c>tux</c> and domain <c>homenetwork</c>. \n"
msgstr "ユーザーが決めなければならない選択の一つは自分のPCの名前です。至極簡単に思えますが<e>多くの</e>ユーザーは自分のLinux-pcに適当な名前を見付けるのに苦労してます。事を早く進めるために、選んだ名前は後で変更できることを知っておいてください。判りやすいように、ここでは単にマシンを<c>tux</c>、ドメイン名を<c>homenetwork</c>と呼ぶことにします。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:194
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Setting the host name"
msgstr "ホスト名を設定"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:195
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>nano -w /etc/conf.d/hostname</i>\n"
"\n"
"<comment>(Set the hostname variable to your host name)</comment>\n"
"hostname=\"<i>tux</i>\"\n"
msgstr ""
"# <i>nano -w /etc/conf.d/hostname</i>\n"
"   \n"
"<comment>(hostname変数に自分のホスト名を設定してください)</comment>\n"
"hostname=\"<i>tux</i>\"\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:202
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Second, <e>if</e> you need a domainname, set it in <path>/etc/conf.d/net</path>.\n"
"You only need a domain if your ISP or network administrator says so, or if you\n"
"have a DNS server but not a DHCP server. You don't need to worry about DNS or\n"
"domainnames if your networking is setup for DHCP.\n"
msgstr ""
"次に、<e>もし</e>ドメイン名が必要なら、<path>/etc/conf.d/net</path>に設定します。\n"
"ISPやネットワーク管理者からそう言われているか、DHCPサーバは持っておらずDNSサーバを持っているときのみドメインが必要になります。\n"
"もしネットワークにつなげるときDHCPの設定を行っていれば、DNSやドメイン名に悩む必要はありません。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:208
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Setting the domainname"
msgstr "domain名を設定"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:209
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>nano -w /etc/conf.d/net</i>\n"
"\n"
"<comment>(Set the dns_domain variable to your domain name)</comment>\n"
"dns_domain_lo=\"<i>homenetwork</i>\"\n"
msgstr ""
"# <i>nano -w /etc/conf.d/net</i>\n"
"   \n"
"<comment>(dns_domain変数に自分のドメイン名を設定してください)</comment>\n"
"dns_domain_lo=\"<i>homenetwork</i>\"\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><note>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:216
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you choose not to set a domainname, you can get rid of the \"This is\n"
"hostname.(none)\" messages at your login screen by editing\n"
"<path>/etc/issue</path>. Just delete the string <c>.\\O</c> from that file.\n"
msgstr ""
"ドメイン名を設定しないことを選択した場合、<path>/etc/issue</path>を編集することで、ログイン画面の\"This is hostname.(none)\"というメッセージを取り除くことができます。\n"
"そのファイルから文字列<c>.\\O</c>を削除するだけです。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:222
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you have a NIS domain (if you don't know what that is, then you don't have\n"
"one), you need to define that one too:\n"
msgstr "もしNISドメインがあれば(これについてわからなければ、それが無いということです)、それも定義しなければなりません。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:226
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Setting the NIS domainname"
msgstr "NISドメイン名を設定"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:227
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>nano -w /etc/conf.d/net</i>\n"
"\n"
"<comment>(Set the nis_domain variable to your NIS domain name)</comment>\n"
"nis_domain_lo=\"<i>my-nisdomain</i>\"\n"
msgstr ""
"# <i>nano -w /etc/conf.d/net</i>\n"
"   \n"
"<comment>(nis_domain変数に自分のNISドメイン名を設定してください)</comment>\n"
"nis_domain_lo=\"<i>my-nisdomain</i>\"\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><note>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-config.xml:234
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"For more information on configuring DNS and NIS, please read the examples\n"
"provided in <path>/usr/share/doc/openrc-*/net.example.bz2</path> which\n"
"can be read using <c>bzless</c>. Also, you may want to emerge <c>openresolv</c>\n"
"to help manage your DNS/NIS setup.\n"
msgstr ""
